{"type": "article", "id": 28992, "title": "模块型收纳架", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-01T06:49:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016070312180692PEIJoaz4tBMeqU.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>面对储物架，人们往往有着相同的顾虑：安装过程繁琐或是担心不够牢固。家具品牌 SWENYO 最近推出了一款采用模块型设计的架子 Wallace：最贴近墙壁的是一道铝合金的固定槽，接着是一块木质夹板。沿着夹板中间的滑动槽，用户可以根据需要放上搁板、小型容器或者是木箱。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/wallace-rethink-shelving--4#/\">众筹链接</a>，基础包的早鸟价为 75 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121804PAo6qhwFRyTU8dDJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73225806\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121805yfCmK6MGuW0Rsrbw.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56935484\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031218067WYN1jaIc3plUuy8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56612903\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}